Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Building Maintenance Services
Bare Metal Standard, Inc. provides janitorial services. The Company offers grease and hood duct, as well as exhaust fan cleaning services. Bare Metal Standard serves customers in the United States.




